###############################################################################
# resilience-lab — 00: health dos dois serviços
# Portas fixadas pelo compose.lab.yml: package-service :8081, logistics-service :8082.
# IntelliJ HTTP Client: selecione o ambiente "lab" (requests/http-client.env.json).
# VS Code REST Client: as variáveis @... abaixo já apontam para os mesmos hosts.
#
# Estes arquivos cobrem só a superfície HTTP do lab. Os passos que vivem no SQS
# (duplicata com mesmo dedup-id, mensagem poison, evento stale forjado) não são
# expressáveis em .http — ver scenarios/*.sh.
###############################################################################
@packageHost = http://localhost:8081
@logisticsHost = http://localhost:8082

### [package-service] Health agregado
GET {{packageHost}}/management/health

### [package-service] Liveness (probe usada pelo lab em wait_healthy)
GET {{packageHost}}/management/health/liveness

### [package-service] Readiness
GET {{packageHost}}/management/health/readiness

### [logistics-service] Health agregado
GET {{logisticsHost}}/management/health

### [logistics-service] Liveness
GET {{logisticsHost}}/management/health/liveness

### [logistics-service] Readiness
GET {{logisticsHost}}/management/health/readiness

### [observabilidade] Gauge de eventos FAILED na outbox do package-service
# outbox.failed.count > 0 = evento esgotou os retries de publicação (intervenção manual)
GET {{packageHost}}/management/metrics/outbox.failed.count

### [observabilidade] Idem no logistics-service
GET {{logisticsHost}}/management/metrics/outbox.failed.count
